WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:02.790
<v ->Hello and welcome to this online course developed for you,</v>

2
00:00:02.790 --> 00:00:06.300
the instructor, to help teach advanced on road cycle skills.

3
00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:08.160
This course has been developed to provide you

4
00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.170
with strategies and examples of good practice

5
00:00:10.170 --> 00:00:12.600
in any cycle training environment.

6
00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:16.830
For example, complex infrastructure, multi-lane roundabouts,

7
00:00:16.830 --> 00:00:18.870
junctions controlled by traffic lights.

8
00:00:18.870 --> 00:00:21.870
This will give you the confidence to do this well.

9
00:00:21.870 --> 00:00:24.210
There's loads of reasons why people may need this training.

10
00:00:24.210 --> 00:00:27.570
They may want to explore the countryside, commute to work,

11
00:00:27.570 --> 00:00:30.840
go for a ride with their family, or go shopping even.

12
00:00:30.840 --> 00:00:32.790
We really do hope you enjoy the training

13
00:00:32.790 --> 00:00:35.207
and learn lots along the way.

